{"type":null,"faqId":35696,"title":"How do I remove the camera button at the bottom-right of the lock screen?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>The camera button at the bottom-right of the lock screen is a convenient feature of the EMUI system that allows users to launch the camera quickly. If you do not require this feature, you can remove it using one of the following methods:</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>Change the theme</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Go to </span><span class=\"s2\">Themes</span><span> and then select a theme that does not contain a camera button on the bottom-right of the lock screen.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>Change the unlock method</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Enter </span><span class=\"s2\">Themes</span><span>, select </span><span class=\"s2\">Customize &gt; Screen lock style</span><span> and then swipe to the left or right to select a style that does not contain a camera button.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>* This solution is only applicable to EMUI 2.0 or above.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"476","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437124675000,"seriesProductName":"G630-U10,G760-L01,Jazz-L09,Jazz-UL00,S7-721u,S7-722u,S8-301u,S8-701u,Sophia-L10,Y221-U22,Y330-U11,Y520-U22,Y600-U20","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"remove, camera button","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}